<p>Ever use a Java app?</p>
<p>One can argue about exactly <i>why</i> a 4GHz, 12-core modern monstrosity is less responsive than a 1980s microcomputer when used in all kinds of everyday ways (word processing, etc.) but the fact remains.</p>
<p>Yours,<br />
-Stanislav</p>

